yingyinNormal.en: And there's that moment when you're at the top when you just don't know if you're gonna return back to Earth.
yingyinNormal.zh: 荡到高处，鬼才知道会不会返回地球。

yingyinNormal.en: Why didn't you attempt to return to LaGuardia? There simply was not enough altitude.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你为什么不尝试返回拉瓜迪亚机场？显然没有足够的高度。

yingyinNormal.en: There was enough altitude and speed after the bird strike for a successful return to LaGuardia. Successful? The plane landed at LaGuardia. Intact. Undamaged.
yingyinNormal.zh: 在鸟击过后，飞机有足够的高度和速度可以成功返回拉瓜迪亚机场。成功返回？飞机降落在拉瓜迪亚机场完好无缺，未有损坏。

yingyinNormal.en: If I do not lead this next assault, my men will return north, and I with them.
yingyinNormal.zh: 如果这次进攻不由我带领的话，我的人马会返回北方，我也会和他们一起回去。

yingyinNormal.en: Okay, you need to return to LaGuardia? Turn left heading 2-2-0. 2-2-0. Which engine did you lose? Both. Both engines.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好的，你需要返回拉瓜迪亚？左转航向220。航向220。哪台发动机停车？双发，双发停车。

yingyinNormal.en: Every computer simulation with the exact flight parameters demonstrated that a return to LaGuardia was possible. And not just possible, probable.
yingyinNormal.zh: 每个计算机模拟都使用同样的飞行参数，证明返回拉瓜迪亚机场是可能的，而且不只是可能，是可行的。

yingyinNormal.en: Attention. Return to start positions. Return to start positions.
yingyinNormal.zh: 注意，回到初始位置，回到初始位置。

yingyinNormal.en: I must return to the line.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我必须回到前线去了。

yingyinNormal.en: Sentinel Prime. We bid you return.
yingyinNormal.zh: 御天敌，我们欢迎你回来。

yingyinNormal.en: I return to town tomorrow. So soon?
yingyinNormal.zh: 我明天就回城了。这么快？

yingyinNormal.en: Yee! Should I return the boutonniere?
yingyinNormal.zh: 哎呀！我要不要把胸花退回去？

yingyinNormal.en: What? Are you kidding? I can't return this.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你怎么会知道我要这个呢？什么？你在开玩笑吗？我不能退还这个的。

yingyinNormal.en: The rains will return and the river will rise.
yingyinNormal.zh: 雨季会再来，河面将升高。

yingyinNormal.en: Run away, Simba. Run. Run away and never return.
yingyinNormal.zh: 跑的远远的，辛巴快跑，跑的远远的，再也不要回来了。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm afraid there are ways in which he can return.
yingyinNormal.zh: 恐怕他有许多办法可以回来。

yingyinNormal.en: Claire, you wouldn't return my calls. I'll be back.
yingyinNormal.zh: Claire你不回我电话。我就回来。

yingyinNormal.en: Slick. You never did return that stapler, by the way.
yingyinNormal.zh: 真狡猾，那个订书机还没还我呢，对了。

yingyinNormal.en: Tadashi's gone. When will he return? He is dead, Baymax.
yingyinNormal.zh: 阿正走了。他什么时候回来？他死了，大白。

yingyinNormal.en: Return the boats!
yingyinNormal.zh: 把船划回来。

yingyinNormal.en: So why did you return my call? Because it's the Red Sox.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那你干嘛还回我电话？因为红袜队的名气。

word_usage.usage:
return是瞬间动词，不可与表示一段时间的状语连用。
示例：我回家已经一周了。
误 I have returned home for a week.
正 I returned home a week ago.
正 It is a week since I returned home.

return本身就表示回去或回来，因而不与again或back连用。
示例：他快回来了。
误 He'll return back soon.
误 He'll return again soon.
正 He'll return soon.

sense_info_list.en: come or go back to a previous place

examination_example.sentence: Perhaps a <highlight>return</highlight> to real cooking needn't be far off.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 也许距回归实际存在的烹饪并不遥远。

examination_example.sentence: And based on past experiences, it takes four to five years after economic recovery for unemployment to <highlight>return</highlight> to pre-crisis levels.

examination_example.sentence: She <highlight>returned</highlight> it to its owner right away.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 她马上把它还给了主人。

examination_example.sentence: A waiter has <highlight>returned</highlight> a check worth nearly $424, 000 to the retired social worker who lost it.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 一名服务员将一张价值近42.4万美元的支票退还给了丢失支票的退休社会工作者。

return本身就表示回去或回来，因而不与again或back连用。
示例：他快回来了。
误 He'll return back soon.
误 He'll return again soon.
正 He'll return soon.

return是瞬间动词，不可与表示一段时间的状语连用。
示例：我回家已经一周了。
误 I have returned home for a week.
正 I returned home a week ago.
正 It is a week since I returned home.

精选各省市考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2018-2021年4年间全国各省市中考试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

sense_info_list.en: come or go back to a previous place

examination_example.sentence: Lee has helped the local people sell their products since he <highlight>returned</highlight> to his hometown.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 自从李回到家乡，他就帮助当地人销售他们的产品。

examination_example.sentence: As days went on, I was nervous about <highlight>returning</highlight> to work.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 随着时间的推移，我对重返工作感到紧张。

examination_example.sentence: In 1935, he <highlight>returned</highlight> to China and helped fight against the Japanese army.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 1935年，他回到中国，帮助抗击日军。

sense_info_list.en: send, take, give, put, or others something back to where it came from

examination_example.sentence: However, the woman decided to <highlight>return</highlight> the parrot to the store the next day.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 然而，这位女士决定第二天把鹦鹉还给商店。

examination_example.sentence: Kate <highlight>returned</highlight> the bike on time.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 凯特准时归还了自行车。

examination_example.sentence: To our surprise, he <highlight>returned</highlight> us the change!
examination_example.sentence_trans: 令我们吃惊的是，他把找的零钱还给了我们!

sense_info_list.en: give, do, or get something after something similar has been given or done to you

examination_example.sentence: One day I will <highlight>return</highlight> your help.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 总有一天我会回报你的帮助。

examination_example.sentence: Give our love, though we sometimes get nothing in <highlight>return</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我们要付出我们的爱，尽管有时我们得不到任何回报。

examination_example.sentence: In <highlight>return</highlight>, we should understand and care about them.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 作为回报，我们应该理解和关心他们。

sense_info_list.en: happen again, go back to a previous state

examination_example.sentence: With the whole country's joint efforts, I have <highlight>returned</highlight> to normal.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 在全国人民的共同努力下，我已恢复正常。

word_usage.usage:
return是瞬间动词，不可与表示一段时间的状语连用。
示例：我回家已经一周了。
误 I have returned home for a week.
正 I returned home a week ago.
正 It is a week since I returned home.

return本身就表示回去或回来，因而不与again或back连用。
示例：他快回来了。
误 He'll return back soon.
误 He'll return again soon.
正 He'll return soon.
